### Create New User
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "raju",
  "password": "raju",
  "email": "raju@gmail.com",
  "age": 20
}


### User Login
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/auth
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "raju@gmail.com",
  "password": "raju"
}


