### Update User by ID
PUT http://localhost:4000/user-api/users/69b41abb9912bbfa6ba9050a
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manoj",
  "password": "manoj",
  "email": "manoj@gmail.com",
  "age": 22
}


### Delete User by ID
DELETE http://localhost:4000/user-api/users/USER_OBJECT_ID


### Create Product
POST http://localhost:4000/product-api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "productName": "Mobile",
  "price": 20000,
  "brand": "Samsung"
}


### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:4000/product-api/products


### Get Product by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/product-api/products/69b41b2c9912bbfa6ba90510


### Update Product by ID
PUT http://localhost:4000/product-api/products/69b41b2c9912bbfa6ba90510
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productName": "Samsung Galaxy",
  "price": 25000,
  "brand": "Samsung"
}


### Delete Product by ID
DELETE http://localhost:4000/product-api/products/69b41b2c9912bbfa6ba90510


